Installation:

Unix/linux:

> git clone git://github.com/rhardey/vimfiles.git ~/.vim
> ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
> ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
> git submodule update --init
        
Windows:

In the home folder:

NOTE: I've had all sorts of grief with symlinks in Windows so have given up trying to use them.

> git clone git://github.com/rhardey/vimfiles.git %HOME%\vimfiles
> echo source ~/vimfiles/vimrc > %HOME%/.vimrc
> echo source ~/vimfiles/gvimrc > %HOME%/.gvimrc
> git submodule update --init

